opinion.posture: Motion of defendant to remand indictments 74-656 and 74-657 for the purpose of a hearing in Superior Court granted. Upon completion of the hearing the indictments shall be returned immediately to this court.

Julius C. Michaelson, Attorney General, for plaintiff.
